      • loadPrincipal

        public static Optional<Principal> loadPrincipal(Authenticator authenticator,
                                                String username)
        Gets the principal with the given username from the given Authenticator.
        Parameters:
        authenticator - the Authenticator to use for reading the principal information
        username - the name of the Principal to read
        Returns:
        the read Principal object. This method does not return null.
        Throws:
        NoSuchElementException - if the principal could not be loaded.
